    <briefdescription>
<para>Information about a received periodic advertising report. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This struct holds information about a periodic advertising event that has been received. It contains details such as the advertiser’s address, SID, transmit power, RSSI, CTE type, and additional information depending on the configuration (e.g., event counter and subevent in case of a subevent indication). This information is provided in the callback when periodic advertising data is received.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Used in <ref refid="structbt__le__per__adv__sync__cb" kindref="compound">bt_le_per_adv_sync_cb</ref> structure. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
